  "title": "Warehouse Storekeeper",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>Pharmline Marketing Pte Ltd is a sales, marketing and distribution company for healthcare and pharmaceutical products.  We represent some of the top brands. We supply to GPs, specialist clinics, chain and indepenent pharmacies, hospitals, nursing homes and other healthcare institutions.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will manage the receipt, inspection, storage, and dispatch of healthcare products to ensure accurate order fulfillment and maintain a clean, organized warehouse environment.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Inspect incoming shipments by verifying goods against shipping documents and assessing product condition to ensure accuracy and quality</li><li>Store received goods systematically to optimize warehouse space and facilitate easy retrieval</li><li>Pack and label products accurately according to customer requirements to prepare orders for shipment</li><li>Select and pick items from inventory based on picking lists to fulfill customer orders efficiently</li><li>Coordinate the release of packed goods to transport companies to ensure timely delivery</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and orderliness in the warehouse to support a safe and efficient work environment</li></ul>",
